PRACTICAL 9: Managing Virtual Machines
Prerequisites

â€¢ All previous practicals completed

Steps

Log in to vCenter Server.

Unregister a virtual machine from inventory.

Navigate to datastore and register the virtual machine again.

Delete a virtual machine permanently from datastore if required.

Take snapshot of a virtual machine before changes.

Modify VM files and take additional snapshots.

Revert virtual machine to a previous snapshot.

Delete individual snapshots or all snapshots.

Verify virtual machine state after snapshot operations.
